---
import Layout from "@/layouts/layout.astro";
import { MaskedHeading } from "@/components/typography/masked-heading";

---

<Layout title="Referral">
  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-10">
      <MaskedHeading
        id="referral-name"
        className="animate-slide-in opacity-0 max-w-4xl text-5xl sm:text-7xl lg:text-[5.5rem] leading-[1.1]"
      >
        Hey,
      </MaskedHeading>
    </div>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col max-w-4xl items-center">
      <p class="text-xl">
        I wanted to share some exciting news with youâ€”I've recently started my own company <b>NodeFlux Pte Ltd</b>! It's been an incredible journey so far, and I'm really excited about the opportunities ahead.</p>

        <p class="text-xl mt-5">
        I'm currently looking to connect with potential clients who might need any of the following services (and more):
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 text-md mb-5">
        <li>Website development</li>
        <li>Application development (both mobile and web)</li>
        <li>Graphic design</li>
        <li>AI workflow automation</li>
        <li>Social media presence</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        If you know anyone who might benefit from these services, I would be incredibly grateful if you could pass along my contact information.

        In return, I've set up a referral system for some close friends. Here's how it works:
      </p>

      <!-- Referral Tiers Table -->
      <table class="table-auto border-collapse border border-gray-400 mt-4">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">If the client spends ($)</th>
            <th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Your Referral Fee($)</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">$1000 to $2999</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">$100</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">$3000 to $4999</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">$300</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">$5000 to $7499</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">$500</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">$7500 to $9999</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">$750</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">$10000 onwards</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">$1000</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      
      <p class="mt-3">
        Also, I would really appreciate it if you could follow NodeFlux's Socials as well. As a valued friend, your support means a lot to me.
      </p>
      <div class="flex item-center gap-4">
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/nodefluxsg" class="h-11 w-11 rounded-full border grid place-items-center">
          <img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65b815fb8b11393078dd199d/65e08a7ccb4f3f1f41f327f3_linedin%20icon.svg" />
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://www.facebook.com/people/NodeFlux-Pte-Ltd/61565335343560/"
          class="h-11 w-11 rounded-full border grid place-items-center"
        >
          <img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65b815fb8b11393078dd199d/65e08a7ccb4f3f1f41f327f1_facebook%20icon.svg" />
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/nodefluxsg/" class="h-11 w-11 rounded-full border grid place-items-center">
          <img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65b815fb8b11393078dd199d/65e08a7ccb4f3f1f41f327f2_instagram%20icon.svg" />
        </a>
        <a href="https://x.com/nodefluxsg?lang=en" class="h-11 w-11 rounded-full border grid place-items-center">
          <img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65b815fb8b11393078dd199d/65e08a7ccb4f3f1f41f327f4_twitter%20icon.svg" />
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Terms and Conditions -->
      <div class="mt-8" style="color: #7d7d7d;">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold ">Terms and Conditions</h2>
        <p class="text-sm">
          The referral program is subject to the following terms:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 text-sm">
          <li>This offer is valid for 1 year from 16-Sep-2024 to 15-Sep-2025.</li>
          <li>Referral rewards are applicable only after successful referral and completion of client's project.</li>
          <li>Rewards will be given within 30 days of final payment confirmation from referred clients.</li>
          <li>NodeFlux Pte. Ltd. reserves the right to amend or terminate this offer at any time without prior notice.</li>
          <li>In case of any dispute, the NodeFlux Pte. Ltd.'s decision will be final and binding.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Client-side Script -->
  <script>
    // Wait until the page is fully loaded
    window.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', (event) => {
      // Get the URL query parameters
      const urlParams = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
      const fullName = urlParams.get('name')?.replace(/\+/g, " ") || "Valued Friend";
      
      // Update the referral name dynamically
      const nameElement = document.getElementById('referral-name');
      if (nameElement) {
        nameElement.textContent = `Hey ${fullName},`;
      }
    });
  </script>
</Layout>